Plot parameter estimation iterations

Source: R/plotTrace.R
plotTrace.Rd

Plot parameter estimation iterations

Usage

plotTrace(file.mod, pars = NULL, label.by = "parameter", col.label = NULL, ...)

Arguments

file.mod

NONMEM model file, must be completed run

pars

a parameter table to map NONMEM parameters to their labels

label.by

a column in the parameter table which will be used for merging the parameter table and the parameter labels in the .ext file, as read by `NMdata::NMreadExt()`. usually this column is 'parameter' and has values such as 'THETA1', 'THETA2', .... , 'OMEGA(1,1)', 'OMEGA(2,2)', ... 'SIGMA(1,1)', etc.

col.label

the column in the parameter table which we will use for labeling the plot panels.

...

Passed to `NMdata::NMreadExt()`.
